<div class="floatnone"><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:Goya-Guerra_(70).jpg" class="image" title="Plate 70: No saben el camino (They do not know the way). A long line of male prisoners extending for a great distance, bound together with rope, walk across a mountainous countryside."><img alt="A long line of male prisoners extending for a great distance all tied together with ropes, traipse across the mountainous countryside. Some are priests most in civilian clothes." src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/0/0f/Goya-Guerra_(70).jpg/160px-Goya-Guerra_(70).jpg" width="160" height="115" class="thumbborder" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/0/0f/Goya-Guerra_%2870%29.jpg/240px-Goya-Guerra_%2870%29.jpg 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/0/0f/Goya-Guerra_%2870%29.jpg/320px-Goya-Guerra_%2870%29.jpg 2x" /></a></div>
</div>
