<div class="center">
<div class="floatnone"><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:Goya-Guerra_(71).jpg" class="image" title="Plate 71: Contra el bien general (Against the common good). A monstrous winged devil sits upon a rock and writes a book, perhaps a book of fate, or a book of evil."><img alt="Sitting on a rock, a monstrous winged devil writes a book, perhaps a book of fate, or a book of evil." src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/e/e4/Goya-Guerra_(71).jpg/160px-Goya-Guerra_(71).jpg" width="160" height="115" class="thumbborder" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/e/e4/Goya-Guerra_%2871%29.jpg/240px-Goya-Guerra_%2871%29.jpg 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/e/e4/Goya-Guerra_%2871%29.jpg/320px-Goya-Guerra_%2871%29.jpg 2x" /></a></div>
</div>
