<tr style="vertical-align:top;">
<td style="display:block; font-size:1em; height:10.7em; padding:0px;">
<div class="gallerytext" style="height:10.6em; width:167px; line-height:1.3em; padding:2px 6px 1px 6px; overflow-y:auto; margin:0px; border:none; border-width:0px;">Plate 71: <i>Contra el bien general</i> (<i>Against the common good</i>). A monstrous winged devil sits upon a rock and writes a book, perhaps a book of fate, or a book of evil. &#160;</div>
